A possible workaround is to add the css with javascript

```
$(function() {
            setTimeout(function() {
                var $head = $(".cke_wysiwyg_frame").contents().find("head");
                var url = "{% static '<PATH-TO-YOUR-CSS>' %}";
                $head.append($("<link/>", { rel: "stylesheet", href: url, type: "text/css" } ));
            }, 2000); // Wait for CKEditor to init
        });
```

Where `.cke_wysiwyg_frame` is the class of the iframe.

